snippet.title: Gartic On Stream | Interactive game for streamers
snippet.description:
Access: https://gos.gg

The livestreams could and should be more interactive! With that in mind we brought the fun from Gartic to the livestreams! Now everyone who watches the streams can also play through the chats on Twitch, Mixer ou YouTube.
